<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="hr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Ulaganje u infrastrukturu | NK Polet Sveta Klara</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/Logo/657d031c9cf70ae04f623d076157e09ff63013fb.png">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Barlow+Condensed:wght@400;500;600;700;800;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root { --blue: #1B2A4A; --red: #D42428; --red-l: #E84E52; --dark: #0F1520; --light: #F7F7F8; --white: #FFFFFF; }
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; background: var(--light); color: var(--dark); line-height: 1.7; }

        .progress-bar { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; height: 4px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--red), var(--red-l)); width: 0%; z-index: 9999; transition: width 0.1s linear; }
        .back-link { position: fixed; top: 82px; left: 20px; z-index: 100; background: rgba(15,21,32,0.7); backdrop-filter: blur(10px); color: var(--white); text-decoration: none; padding: 10px 20px; border-radius: 30px; font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 0.9rem; letter-spacing: 0.5px; transition: all 0.3s ease; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }
        .back-link:hover { background: var(--red); transform: translateX(-3px); }
        .back-link svg { width: 16px; height: 16px; }

        .article-hero { position: relative; width: 100%; height: 60vh; min-height: 450px; overflow: hidden; }
        .article-hero img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
        .hero-overlay { position: absolute; inset: 0; background: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(15,21,32,0.3) 0%, rgba(15,21,32,0.5) 50%, rgba(15,21,32,0.95) 100%); }
        .hero-content { position: absolute; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; padding: 60px 40px 50px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
        .category-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--red); color: var(--white); font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.75rem; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .article-meta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; margin-bottom: 16px; }
        .hero-title { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 800; font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem); color: var(--white); line-height: 1.1; text-transform: uppercase; }

        .article-body { max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px 80px; position: relative; }
        .article-body::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 60px; height: 4px; background: var(--red); border-radius: 2px; }
        .article-body p { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #333; margin-bottom: 24px; text-align: justify; }
        .article-body p:first-of-type::first-letter { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 3.5rem; font-weight: 800; float: left; line-height: 1; margin-right: 10px; margin-top: 4px; color: var(--red); }

        .article-body h2 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.6rem; color: var(--blue); text-transform: uppercase; margin: 40px 0 16px; padding-left: 16px; border-left: 4px solid var(--red); }

        .info-card { background: var(--dark); border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px; margin: 40px 0; color: var(--white); }
        .info-card h3 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--red-l); margin-bottom: 20px; text-align: center; }
        .info-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
        .info-item { text-align: center; padding: 16px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border-radius: 8px; }
        .info-item .number { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-weight: 700; font-size: 2rem; color: var(--red-l); }
        .info-item .label { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-size: 0.85rem; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; margin-top: 4px; }

        .timeline { margin: 40px 0; padding-left: 30px; border-left: 3px solid var(--red); }
        .timeline-item { margin-bottom: 28px; position: relative; }
        .timeline-item::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: -37px; top: 6px; width: 14px; height: 14px; background: var(--red); border-radius: 50%; border: 3px solid var(--light); }
        .timeline-item .date { font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--red); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .timeline-item .desc { font-size: 0.95rem; color: #555; }

        .decoration-dots { text-align: center; margin: 30px 0; color: var(--red); font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; font-size: 1.2rem; letter-spacing: 12px; }
        .share-section { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; padding: 30px 0; border-top: 2px solid var(--light); margin-top: 40px; }
        .share-section span { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #999; font-size: 0.85rem; }
        .share-btn { width: 40px; height: 40px; border-radius: 50%; border: 2px solid #ddd; background: none; cursor: pointer; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.3s ease; color: #666; }
        .share-btn:hover { border-color: var(--red); background: var(--red); color: var(--white); }

        .site-footer { background: var(--dark); color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); padding: 60px 24px 30px; }
        .footer-inner { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 40px; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; }
        .footer-brand { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; }
        .footer-brand img { width: 50px; height: 50px; object-fit: contain; }
        .footer-brand-text h4 { font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif; font-weight: 700; color: var(--white); font-size: 1.1rem; text-transform: uppercase; }
        .footer-brand-text p { font-size: 0.8rem; }
        .footer-info p { font-size: 0.85rem; margin-bottom: 4px; }
        .footer-bottom { max-width: 900px; margin: 40px auto 0; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1); text-align: center; font-size: 0.8rem; font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace; }

        /* Nav */
        .nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:1000;height:72px;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 48px;transition:all .4s;background:rgba(11,15,24,.94);backdrop-filter:blur(20px);border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
        .ni{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;width:100%}
        .nav-left{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:40px}
        .nav-brand{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px;text-decoration:none}
        .nav-crest{width:52px;height:52px;flex-shrink:0}.nav-crest img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:contain}
        .nav-name{font-family:'Barlow Condensed',sans-serif;font-size:1.3rem;font-weight:700;color:#fff;letter-spacing:.1em}
        .nav-links{display:flex;gap:28px;list-style:none}
        .nav-links a{font-size:.78rem;font-weight:600;color:rgba(113,125,143,.9);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.08em;transition:color .3s;text-decoration:none;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}
        .nav-links a:hover{color:#fff}
        .nav-right{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px}
        .nav-social a{width:32px;height:32px;border-radius:8px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:rgba(113,125,143,.9);transition:all .3s;text-decoration:none}
        .nav-social a:hover{color:#fff;background:rgba(255,255,255,.06)}
        .nav-toggle{display:none;flex-direction:column;gap:5px;cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;padding:5px;z-index:1001}
        .nav-toggle span{width:20px;height:1.5px;background:#fff;transition:all .3s;border-radius:1px}
        .nav-toggle.active span:nth-child(1){transform:rotate(45deg) translate(4.5px,4.5px)}
        .nav-toggle.active span:nth-child(2){opacity:0}
        .nav-toggle.active span:nth-child(3){transform:rotate(-45deg) translate(4.5px,-4.5px)}
        @media(max-width:1024px){
        .nav{padding:0 20px}
        .nav-toggle{display:flex;z-index:10001}
        .nav-links{position:fixed;inset:0;background:rgba(11,15,24,.97);flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:32px;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .4s;z-index:10000}
        .nav-links.open{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
        .nav-links a{font-size:1.3rem}
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero-content { padding: 40px 20px 30px; }
            .article-body { padding: 40px 20px 60px; }
            .back-link { top: 82px; left: 12px; padding: 8px 14px; font-size: 0.8rem; }
            .footer-inner { flex-direction: column; gap: 24px; }
            .info-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="progress-bar" id="progressBar"></div>

    <%- include('../partials/nav', {currentPage: currentPage}) %>

    <a href="/vijesti" class="back-link">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M19 12H5M12 19l-7-7 7-7"/></svg>
        Vijesti
    </a>

    <article>
        <div class="article-hero">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1600679472829-3044539ce8ed?w=1920&q=85" alt="Sportski centar Polet">
            <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
            <div class="hero-content">
                <div class="category-badge">Klub</div>
                <div class="article-meta">
                    <span>10. ožujka 2026.</span>
                    <span>&bull;</span>
                    <span>6 min čitanja</span>
                </div>
                <h1 class="hero-title">Ulaganje u budućnost: obnova Sportskog centra Polet</h1>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="article-body">
            <p>Sportski centar Polet prolazi kroz značajnu obnovu koja će omogućiti bolje uvjete za sve ekipe kluba i navijače. Vodstvo NK Poleta Sveta Klara već duže vrijeme planira modernizaciju klupske infrastrukture, a sada su ti planovi konačno počeli dobivati konkretan oblik. Projekt obuhvaća nekoliko ključnih područja koja će značajno unaprijediti kvalitetu sportskog života u našoj zajednici.</p>

            <h2>Glavni teren i travnjak</h2>

            <p>Prva faza projekta uključuje kompletnu obnovu glavnog terena. Travnjak će biti u potpunosti zamijenjen novim, kvalitetnijim, koji će omogućiti igru u svim vremenskim uvjetima. Drenažni sustav bit će moderniziran kako bi se spriječilo nakupljanje vode nakon kiše, što je bio čest problem u prošlim sezonama. Također, rasvjeta će biti nadograđena LED reflektorima koji će osigurati uvjete za večernje utakmice i treninge.</p>

            <div class="info-card">
                <h3>Projekt u brojkama</h3>
                <div class="info-grid">
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="number">2</div>
                        <div class="label">Terena za obnovu</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="number">4</div>
                        <div class="label">Nove svlačionice</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="number">200</div>
                        <div class="label">Novih sjedala</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="info-item">
                        <div class="number">2026</div>
                        <div class="label">Godina završetka</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h2>Svlačionice i popratni sadržaji</h2>

            <p>Jedan od najvažnijih dijelova projekta jest izgradnja novih svlačionica. Trenutne svlačionice su zastarjele i ne zadovoljavaju moderne standarde. Nove prostorije bit će opremljene svim potrebnim sadržajima uključujući prostoriju za fizioterapiju, prostoriju za analize utakmica s projektorom, te komfornije tuševe i sanitarne čvorove. Ovi poboljšani uvjeti pokazat će igračima da klub uistinu brine o njima.</p>

            <h2>Plan realizacije</h2>

            <div class="timeline">
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="date">Siječanj 2026.</div>
                    <div class="desc">Početak radova na drenažnom sustavu glavnog terena</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="date">Ožujak 2026.</div>
                    <div class="desc">Postavljanje novog travnjaka i LED rasvjete</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="date">Lipanj 2026.</div>
                    <div class="desc">Početak gradnje novih svlačionica</div>
                </div>
                <div class="timeline-item">
                    <div class="date">Rujan 2026.</div>
                    <div class="desc">Završetak radova i svečano otvorenje</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <p>Predsjednik kluba naglasio je važnost ovog projekta za cijelu zajednicu Svete Klare: "Ovo nije samo ulaganje u nogomet, već u budućnost našeg kraja. Sportski centar Polet bit će mjesto gdje će se generacije mladih sportaša razvijati u kvalitetne igrače i, što je još važnije, u kvalitetne ljude. Zahvalni smo svima koji su podržali ovaj projekt - od Grada Zagreba do naših vjernih navijača i sponzora."</p>

            <div class="decoration-dots">&middot; &middot; &middot;</div>

            <div class="share-section">
                <span>Podijeli</span>
                <button class="share-btn" title="Facebook"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M18 2h-3a5 5 0 00-5 5v3H7v4h3v8h4v-8h3l1-4h-4V7a1 1 0 011-1h3z"/></svg></button>
                <button class="share-btn" title="Twitter"><svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M23 3a10.9 10.9 0 01-3.14 1.53 4.48 4.48 0 00-7.86 3v1A10.66 10.66 0 013 4s-4 9 5 13a11.64 11.64 0 01-7 2c9 5 20 0 20-11.5a4.5 4.5 0 00-.08-.83A7.72 7.72 0 0023 3z"/></svg></button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>

    <footer class="site-footer">
        <div class="footer-inner">
            <div class="footer-brand">
                <img src="/Logo/657d031c9cf70ae04f623d076157e09ff63013fb.png" alt="NK Polet">
                <div class="footer-brand-text">
                    <h4>NK Polet Sveta Klara</h4>
                    <p>Osnovan 1948. godine</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="footer-info">
                <p>Sportski centar Polet</p>
                <p>Sveta Klara, Zagreb</p>
                <p>info@nkpolet.hr</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer-bottom">
            <p>&copy; 2026 NK Polet Sveta Klara. Sva prava pridržana.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>

    <script>
        window.addEventListener('scroll', () => {
            const scrollTop = window.scrollY;
            const docHeight = document.documentElement.scrollHeight - window.innerHeight;
            const progress = (scrollTop / docHeight) * 100;
            document.getElementById('progressBar').style.width = progress + '%';
        });
    </script>
    <%- include('../partials/nav-js') %>
</body>
</html>